http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/DLSA-workshop-inaugurated/article13998386.ece

Chairman of District Legal Services Authority (DLSA) N. Sharanappa inaugurated a two-day training workshop for panel lawyers of the DLSA, jointly conducted by the DLSA and District Advocates association in Yadgir on Wednesday.He called upon the panel lawyers to extend co-operation and create legal awareness among people.Twenty seven lawyers were appointed to the DLSA recently and they have been deployed to various places, including District and Session Court, other taluk courts, tahsil offices, Child Development and Protection Offices, etc.